# No external CDN

**Must:** Do not load runtime assets from third-party CDNs (Google Fonts, gstatic, jsDelivr, unpkg, cdnjs, Bootstrap CDN, etc.).

**Required patterns:**

- **Flutter web:** always `flutter build web --no-web-resources-cdn` and `flutter run --no-web-resources-cdn` for web targets.
- **Web fonts:** use npm packages (e.g. `@fontsource/*`) imported in SCSS/CSS, or files under `wwwroot`/app `assets/`.
- **Libraries:** install via npm/pub and bundle in the build output; no `<script src="https://cdn...">` or `<link href="https://cdn...">`.

**Verify:** run `.\scripts\verify-no-external-cdn.ps1` before release builds.

**Allowed exceptions:** API calls to your own backend, deep links, user-facing external URLs (About links), and map tile APIs configured as product features (not font/script CDNs).
